A rare good old school kungfu movie that would is great for martial arts collectors. Very entertaining with plenty of action..... 
Chang Yi plays a corrupt eunuch general who uses his personal body guards as a hit squad to anyone who apposes his views. Yueh Hua and Chen Mu Chung are 2 japanese swordsmen who join the general's body guards and quickly rise up and cause deception in the ranks.
 This isn't one of my favorite movies but it is action packed and has a little surprise at the end.
